content:
ForestTrustDomainStatus Enum

Definition

Indicates the status of a forest trust relationship.

In this Article

public enum ForestTrustDomainStatus
Inheritance
Object
ValueType
System.Enum
ForestTrustDomainStatus

Fields

Enabled

The forest trust relationship is enabled.
NetBiosNameAdminDisabled

The forest trust NetBIOS record is disabled by administrative action.
NetBiosNameConflictDisabled

The forest trust NetBIOS record is disabled due to a conflict with an existing NetBIOS record.
SidAdminDisabled

The forest trust SID is disabled by administrative action.
SidConflictDisabled

The forest trust SID is disabled due to a conflict with an existing SID.
